                                    <p>Edtech design is the practice of creating the user interface (UI) and user experience (UX) for software-as-a-service applications delivered via the cloud. Unlike single-purpose apps, Edtech products often serve diverse user roles, handle complex data, and support ongoing subscriptions, all of which demand thoughtful, scalable design.</p>
